Critics have been told to stop politicising the NYS Empowerment Programme.Youth CS Sicily Kariuki said the initiative will improve youths&rsquo; lives. &ldquo;This programme is one of the government&rsquo;s flagship projects aimed at achieving Vision 2030. This is not just any other normal project, but one which will bring a positive impact in the lives of our youth,&rdquo; she said.She spoke in Taveta town on Friday when she launched the programme.More than 900 youths from Taveta constituency have joined the programme.Youths will save money through saccos then use the cash to start businesses. &ldquo;There is potential in poultry farming and small-scale industries,&rdquo; Kariuki said.She urged the youth to be role models and not allow themselves to be manipulated by politicians.